Lab for CYSE 445. Provides hands-on experience in security issues of network systems. Issues in ethical hacking, penetration testing, forensics and incident handling and response will be discussed. Notes: This is a hands-on lab course, with short lecture introductions. Offered by Cyber Security Engineering. Limited to two attempts.
